<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/7737> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #7737" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/5> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Monetalis. In MRR 2.442, and Index, 576, refer also to Crawford, RRC 1.259, no. 220, 145 B.C. Crawford would identify him with the tr. pl. before 123 (RE no. 169; MRR 1.513).\n" .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/2988> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #2988" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Named in the Bembinus Ms of the Didascalia of Terence Eun. (see note 1). Dziatzko's dating in 146 (RhM 21 [1866] 66) is doubted by Seidel (FA 79) since it is unlikely that in this period a plebeian and a patrician would be colleagues in this office." .
